messages.content: Comfyui-Yolov8 is a simple Yolov8 plugin for ComfyUI.
To install Comfyui-Yolov8, you need to clone the repository in the 'custom_nodes' directory of ComfyUI using the command 'https://github.com/zcfrank1st/Comfyui-Yolov8.git'.
Where should you place the detect or seg models for Comfyui-Yolov8?
The detect or seg models for Comfyui-Yolov8 should be placed in the 'models/yolov8' directory of ComfyUI.
Is there an example workflow available for Comfyui-Yolov8?
Yes, there is an example workflow available for Comfyui-Yolov8. It can be found in the repository as 'workflow.png'.
